room_description:
Onsite rooms are available once shelter-in-place is lifted. NEW! Survival on Earth depends upon our alliance with the Cosmic Council. Ancient energy orbs unite us and are safely guarded on the Eiffel Tower in Paris. An evil force has destroyed these orbs! Your superpowers are our last hope to regenerate the energy orbs! 

The only intel we have is that gargoyles guard the secret source of the orbs on the Eiffel tower.  

Find the source on the Eiffel Tower! Without them we will spiral into a black hole in 60 minutes! Our agent in Paris is waiting for your help.
